Package org.neo4j.kernel.impl.transaction.log.entry

Class LogEntryParserSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.kernel.impl.transaction.log.entry.LogEntryParserSet
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CheckpointParserSetV4_2, LogEntryParserSetV2_3, LogEntryParserSetV4_0, LogEntryParserSetV4_2
    public abstract class LogEntryParserSet
extends Object
    Set of log entry parsers for a specific version/layout of these entries. Typically such a set contains parsers for log entries such as: START, COMMAND, COMMIT and CHECKPOINT (see LogEntryTypeCodes, where each such type maps to a specific parser. Versioning of commands (see CommandReaderFactory should be detached from versions of this set.
